---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import w3c from "../img/w3c-blue.svg";
import PNotes from "../components/PNotes.astro";
---

<p-slide class="cover center">
  <h1>Cultural accessibility and inclusion</h1>
  <p-fragment
    ><p class="medium-text">What does the WCAG tell us? 🤔</p>
  </p-fragment>
</p-slide>
<p-slide>
  <p
    class="custom-text-size"
    style="--custom-text-size: 0.7em; line-height: 1.6em"
  >
    🌎 WCAG 2.1 and 2.2 include criteria concerning the comprehensibility of
    content, which
    <span class="cover-red-all"
      >depends not only on the user's physical ability</span
    > but also on
    <span class="cover-red-all"
      >their literacy, native language, and cultural context.</span
    >
  </p>
</p-slide>
<p-slide
  class="two-columns"
  timing="500"
  timing-fragment="700"
  autoplay="list-criteria"
>
  <Image src={w3c} alt="wcag-logo" />
  <p-note>
    <p style="font-size: 0.65em">Some criteria to consider:</p>
    <ul class="long-list" style="margin-block-end: 0.3em; font-size: 0.65em">
      <p-fragment timing-start="0"
        ><li>📌 Education level and reading skills</li></p-fragment
      >
      <p-fragment><li>📌 Economic conditions</li></p-fragment>
      <p-fragment><li>📌 Socio-political context</li></p-fragment>
      <p-fragment><li>📌 Cultural background and norms</li></p-fragment>
      <p-fragment><li>📌 Religion and belief systems</li></p-fragment>
    </ul>
  </p-note>
  <PNotes>
    <p>📌 writing: rtl for example</p>
    <p>
      📌 Level of education: Text should be written in a way that a person with
      a <u>lower secondary education level can understand it</u> easily. If the content
      is complex, a simplified version or summary should be provided
    </p>
    <p>📌 Socio-political context: (access to information, censorship)</p>
    <p>
      📌 If abbreviations are used, there must be a way to understand their
      meaning (e.g., tooltips, inline explanations, or expanded forms at the
      first occurrence)
    </p>
  </PNotes>
</p-slide>
<p-slide class="cover-internal">
  <h1 style="margin-block-end: 1em">Some examples</h1>
  ᕙ( •̀ ᗜ •́ )ᕗ
</p-slide>
